*SEISMIC HORIZONTAL FORCE=AhXW
REFERENCE LOAD
*STRUCTURE & OTHER UTILITIES INCLUDING NON STRESSED PIPES
*Multiply R19 with Ah value
*50% Live load (R22) to be considered, so Ah value to be multiplied with 0.5 for Live load
*PIPING
*For R14 use Scale factor m for pipe seismic load, if scale factor is less than 1, consider 1 only, if it is more than 1 consider actual factor.
*For R17 use factor 1.0 for pipe SAM load since it is the SAM load induced by drift but not inertia
